Cell["\<\
The swap test is a quantum computing procedure used to compare the quantum \
states of two quantum registers indirectly. It is commonly used in quantum \
machine learning, quantum search, and quantum state estimation.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->1845840179,ExpressionUUID->"638cc046-68fa-4e4a-9ae6-adb58e969ca7"],

